    "body": "Hi @Maaark we do not have anything builtin with google adwords but we are very interested in the needs you have.\n\nI have no knowledge at all about google adword or the page you linked unfortunately so you will have to explain it to me a bit more in detail what is it you want to achieve.\n\nCan you detail a bit more for example what are the type of calls you would want to do to google adwords and how it relates to instantsearch.js/search?\n\nThanks\n",
